{"tid":1637714,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屠龍策略： 自製顏色水炮","createTime":"2019-10-08T05:21:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T00:53:58.000Z","uid":274747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c5e6b7997a6e194add1b453c1674d21806d61f3a","tid":1637714,"uid":274747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:21:25.000Z","msg":"材料非常簡單：<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">顏色物料（例如printer 墨）+2L雪碧+ 萬樂珠</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n所有材料為日常用品<br />\n<br />\n使用方法：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 可以手動對準噴射角度</span><br />\n專門針對龍體和狗隻眼部，可導致鏡面完全上色，即時失去視野。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">2. 可以遠距離發射</span><br />\n可以遠距離對準盾牌，令所有防具完全上色。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">3. 可以拋物線發射</span><br />\n拋物線的優勢在於0視線下可以進行噴射。<br />\n由於射程非常遠（萬樂珠x1000），已經等於無限潮吹等級，可以拋物線當寵物花灑使用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此類水炮可以遙距發射，中前場也可使用，但必須掌握萬樂珠份量，以達至潮吹地獄。<br />\n<br />\n最後，萬一無用，雪碧和萬樂珠可以作為補充體力之用，一石二鳥。"},{"pid":"9906700353ad34e8bbf85018e50ec86a9c074df5","tid":1637714,"uid":274747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:21:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c60a7c63d2a28b078721751690978844cd59084","tid":1637714,"uid":274747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:22:00.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"694237494dc2f50c9f795227d6fc0b701e0bf332","tid":1637714,"uid":274747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:24:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c12f0453bd3b4d0407528f33044aad296dab27f3","tid":1637714,"uid":274747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:25:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0773e812fc09bb9e3cec4c667840313b7642a80b","tid":1637714,"uid":274747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:32:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0d05838255c695247124057a8f875c57f4abdfcc","tid":1637714,"uid":274747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T00:53:58.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}